doctype html
html(lang="en")
    head
        title Daily Motivational Confirmation
    body
        h1(style="font-family:'Times New Roman, color: black") Daily Motivational Quotes
        p(style="font-size: 22px, font-family:'Times New Roman, color: black") Thank you for subscribing to recieve daily motivational quotes!
        p(style="font-size: 22px, font-family:'Times New Roman, color: black") Motivation reflects something unique about each one of us and allows us to gain valued outcomes like improved performance, enhanced well-being, personal growth, or a sense of purpose.
        p(style="font-size: 22px, font-family:'Times New Roman, color: black") Motivation is a pathway to change our way of thinking, feeling, and behaving.
        p(style="font-size: 22px, font-family:'Times New Roman, color: black") We hope you can find some motivation within these daily quotes.
        footer
          p.no-reply This email was sent from a notification-only address that cannot accept incoming email. Please do not reply to this message.
          p.leaving-question Got your life together?
            a(href="https://quotes-site.herokuapp.com/unsubscribe/" + id).unsubscribe Unsubscribe.
